name: Venom / Eternal Battle
description:
The eternal battle between good and evil in the stories is a fight against our own egos. I have painted my vision of a moment before the collision of the two equal forces.There is a barely visible VENOM word painted into the fire that is between the two enemy heads. The original is a black and white painting I have painted with oil on a wooden board.

I made this artwork for the Talenthouse contest for the upcoming film, Venom: Let There Be Carnage. I have missed the delivery date so I made it a cryptoart 1/100.
